MTN has unveiled its Black Friday 2018 business deals. “From 23-26 November 2018, entrepreneurs have access to a range of MTN Made For Business SIM-only deals, where devices can be added at a reduced cost,” said MTN. “Black Friday is another platform to deliver a bold new digital world to our customers at lower prices, providing more value for less,” said Jacqui O’Sullivan, Executive: Corporate Affairs at MTN South Africa. “This extends beyond consumer deals. It is essential to look at supporting small businesses wherever we can.” MTN’s Black Friday business deals are listed below.